Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.32,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:46.81,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 24 - The Last Day of Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:04.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy managed to overcome everyone's opposition\Ntowards a baby dingo that Ben found. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So she was allowed to raise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it got a bit bigger already, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:12.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even been ten days since we found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see much change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I still think it got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I tell you, he's a little bigger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You made this up, dintcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:25.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you spot where exactly\Nis Little different from a normal dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would tell you it's a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:30.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then Little is a dog!\NI'm certain it's no different from a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:33.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Ben said it's a dingo pup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging around Little again? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We needed your share of bricks done by yesterday! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've kneaded the clay long ago. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to use up\Nthat amount fully, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:58.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But my share is just twenty bricks!\NI won't do any more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also stop once I've done my fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:04.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell me you can make\Nas many as we need, be it one or two hundred? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:08.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm just telling you, if the amount of clay\Nmixed with straw is slightly over the quota, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,you make it all into bricks, so that nothing is wasted!  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:15.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't you just say that you kneaded\Na lot of clay already? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I never said that.\NThere's about thirty five bricks' worth of clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But dad said just making\Nfifteen a day would be enough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you refusing to work even that little, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I never said I'm refusing to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just that I want a bit more time to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that Clara is entertaining right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate should know, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um. It's about that matter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um. That matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:51.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already! Why do you\Nhave to be so nasty, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna know, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you right away, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What Clara is considering now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:02.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, sister is working\Non an educational course for Lucy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's an educational course?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you don't even understand\Nthe meaning of "educational course"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand! It has something to do\Nwith studying, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:17.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely. Because you don't go to school, she's weighing other ways to get you to learn various important things. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's just evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:20.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's evil about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's evil to only make me continue to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's the same for Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then you do it too, Ben! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I have the time for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we moved here,\Nall I do is one work after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just go and make some bricks already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The clay that I kneaded\Nwith so much effort is going dry! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a silly one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Telling Ben to go study, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Ben would've liked some education,\Nhe can't get any!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:07.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never believe someone that crackers actually exists! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what Ben wants to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably a peasant after our father, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:21.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! He wants to become a carpenter,\Njust like Billy's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he's such a handy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? A doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:37.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:41.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But suppose it... Suppose it...\NHe - a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's really not one bit funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't become a doctor\Nif you don't go to school, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's ultimately pointless,\Nhowever much he wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know of some other way to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going to study in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:06.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If he returns to England to study there,\Nhe can become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:09.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But after we went to all this trouble\Nto come to Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:12.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,there's no reason for him\Nto return to England, is there? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:18.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A trip back would cost a fortune. But then,\Nyou'd also need the money to enroll in a school there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:22.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought. It's best that Ben quits dreaming\Nof something so unattainable, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:28.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's about me - is that true they're going\Nto make me study again? What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel no hunger\Nfor knowledge whatsoever? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I don't. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? No. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:02.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've been producing milk at an unabated rate.\NI'm really impressed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Pansy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You found something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What now, it's just you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You want to come inside too, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't let you in, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably nothing would happen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:39.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in trouble, should something extraordinary\Nhappen to Sticky, who's giving us so much milk. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah! Look out! I nearly stepped on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're still so thirsty for Sticky's milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're a smart one, aren't you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're going to make it into a clinic, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it's best that we don't place it\Ntoo far from the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds reasonable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If it's far from the house,\Nit doesn't sound very practical either. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you decided already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,where to build it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Well if you ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:37.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say we should think of future patients,\Ncoming to Doctor's clinic and build it next to the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But before anything else,\Nit would be Ben's house. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just receiving accommodations there, that's all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:45.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you should prioritize\NBen's comfort above mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:48.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which implies building it\Nas close as possible to the existing house. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's how you see it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, what's your call? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:57.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My line of thought aligns with dad's.\NThis seems like the best place. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Doc?\NShould we build it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I guess, in that case, I don't mind here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:04.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But remember, it's the brick house\Nyou're building - a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's just bricks dried in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Almost like a house from mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A house of mud?\NWorks by me as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:23.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You two helping to make bricks\Nis becoming a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've been trying our best\Nnot to stain our clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you really did,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't change the fact\Nyou need to go change now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've exceeded our quota today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause Ben kneaded way too much of clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:45.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where else? Inside the house to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:47.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With your hands and feet like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, shucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wash them clean over there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go wash them in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:55.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:00.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Instead of drawing water from the well,\Nyou go there to do the washing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, see that Lucy-May\Nwashes herself clean, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:03.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:09.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,These would do, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? And what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy made these, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:30.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Gonna have to remake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So irresponsible, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! C-c-cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The water is so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Like it's supposed to be in autumn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This place has its own autumn and winter, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought it's going to be warm all year round!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:18.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true that we've not seen\Nany cold days in eternity! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was summer back in England,\Nit was also pretty warm aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time we arrived to Australia,\Nit was summer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's like one long, long summer\Nhas come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh no! I got my clothes wet, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:32.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go in? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:37.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we do this... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We won't have to... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:50.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do laundry... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Separately. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,B-but it's so c-cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be all right, Little.\NWait just a minute more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:08.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've done it... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There! Have more! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:11.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Comment: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:14.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Comment: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:17.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah! It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Too weak! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks who's speaking! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Little! You stay there! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't need to get in the water, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike when it-t w-was warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,M-My c-clothes won't go dry at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But at least, you won't have\Nto do the laundry now, would you, sis? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:05.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you two seriously think\Nyou can make your clothes any cleaner this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to wash them, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, would you look at that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you to wash them, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:22.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, you didn't need any cleaning in the first place. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:31.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, how far do you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:35.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have to be far at all.\NJust any place where there's plenty of grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't bring along a stake,\Nwe won't have anything to tie them to. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:44.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But will you be able\Nto hammer the stake into the ground? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:46.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find a stake and a stake hammer? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:55.49,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,On the hill, where cockatoos tweet
Comment: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:59.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:03.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,We'll sit down and spread out our lunch 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:08.00,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey mother, I'm begging you 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:12.21,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,After I'm done helping you, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:16.24,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,And the Christmas bell will ring far and wide, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:20.49,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Please let me go to the lake with everyone 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:25.10,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be good? Sounds good, doesn't it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.53,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Tell me, mother 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Around here should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:31.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:33.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it in place! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was because of soft ground just now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I can't do it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, need you to hold this stake for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you're going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well if that thing lands on my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's all that nonsense? It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already. Just hold the stake steady, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Umhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. Can let go of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:37.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:40.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:46.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That should do, Lucy.\NI drove it pretty deep in. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd think you're actually that strong!\NShould be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But make sure you tie them real tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me with this.\NI learned it from John back on the ship -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,a clove hitch that'll never untie. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He must've already arrived back to England by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:05.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'll move to Australia as well,\Nbut I wonder if he'll actually come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well Clara sure as heck believes he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:12.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose John may also become\Nour new brother at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while since they've last eaten fresh grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:22.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Look how sleepy Little is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, I'm sure some wild hares are living in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go catch one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wild hares aren't supposed to be\Nall that fast on the run. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:36.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for not helping in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't want a patient\Nto see you mud-caked, should one show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty commendable of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:00.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't ever complain and just do the work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In a stark contrast with your\Nuncontrollable little sisters.  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's because the girls are still too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Kate is just two years\Nyounger than you, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:21.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only that wouldn't bother you too much,\Nat least at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Or even only when you have the free time at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you mind giving me lessons\Nevery now and then? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:33.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For example, I have this textbook on Latin grammar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't understand a word of it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Latin, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:42.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, those who study to become doctors\Nare all made to learn Latin, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They do... Learn Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please teach it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:50.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I wasn't boozing so much,\NI probably could have taught you a little Latin. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But alas, it's not an option now.\NI've forgotten all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, try to recollect some of it, Doctor! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I could recollect it,\NI would've done it long ago. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't remember. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you have the time, show me\Nthat textbook on Latin grammar, will you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows if I don't end up recollecting some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split in two to attack from both sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You go that way, I go this way. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:33.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Kate, where exactly is that rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How could you not see it yet, you dunce?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that's 'cause you kept...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:38.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's enough!\NIf the rabbit spots you, it'll slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! We pounce on it simultaneously,\Non my cue. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eck... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:14.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:33.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:54.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That is no rabbit.\NLooks like a kangaroo, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is a kangaroo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So the kangaroos are real, after all? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A very odd fella, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, it doesn't seem to mind us one bit. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:07.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I see an animal this bizarre,\NI just want to collect as many of them as I can, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd suggest you give up on such a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:19.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That kangaroo appears so calm simply because it's in the middle of this spacious prairie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:22.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were to confine it inside a tiny enclosure,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,that would definitely drive it nuts. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:31.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What you mean to say is,\NI should consider the kangaroo's happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a must for someone\Ncalling herself an animal-lover. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:39.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be happier in your keeping, or would it\Nbe happier pounding the earth in the free? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:41.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:47.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So much of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go there to look closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:04.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:06.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:07.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard Little just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:12.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:14.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've strayed rather far from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:15.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:16.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:25.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't have left Little there untied. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:27.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we need to tie Little down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:29.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good if so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:31.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Little had found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:35.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now aren't you a bright one?\NTo figure out we went this way. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:36.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:41.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like he's showing us the way to somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose he can actually be {\i1}that{\i0} smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:50.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is bad! Sticky is not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:53.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She took the stake with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:00.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:00.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:14.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our baby dingo, Little turned out to be\Nway smarter than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:08.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While I tried to surprise brother,\Nhe drops his textbook on Latin into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:10.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, brother. Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:14.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"When I'm Out of Luck...".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.92,0:24:16.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
